query: SELECT COUNT(*) as total_staff, (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM adminPermissions ap INNER JOIN users u ON ap.userId = u.id WHERE u.role = 'staff_admin') as staff_with_perms FROM users WHERE role = 'staff_admin';
